AxFormControl.Name: FormStaticTextControl1
AxFormControl.Text: When ArrangeMethod=Vertical then Columns=Auto just results in a single column.

AxFormControl.Name: FormStaticTextControl1Copy1
AxFormControl.Text: ArrangeMethod=Vertical gives Columns as wide as the widest content. Settings applied to content group below.

AxFormControl.Name: FormStaticTextControl1Copy1Copy1
AxFormControl.Text: ArrangeMethod=HorizontalWrap creates minimum sized columns (280px) and content wraps horizontally within that. If ColumnsMode=Auto, then the content will wrap at bottom of page. Settings applied to content group below.

AxFormControl.Name: FormStaticTextControl1Copy1Copy1Copy1
AxFormControl.Text: ArrangeMethod=HorizontalWrap creates minimum sized columns (280px) and content wraps horizontally within that. If ColumnsMode=Fixed, then the content is distributed across those two columns. Settings applied to content group below.

AxFormControl.Name: Group
AxFormControl.Caption: HeightMode=Auto - pushed to the bottom by the SizeToAvailable group above
